dc.title: Congressman Trent Franks, 2nd Congressional District of Arizona - Homepage
dc.description: Congressman Trent Franks represents Arizona in the U.S. House of Representatives. Trent is a conservative Reagan Republican, and he has spent most of his life working on children's issues and trying to build a better future for all children.
